    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-06-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-06-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="51"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d51">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_LFAWD1">Leahy</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 51 <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_THS1" type="from"
                            >Truman</persName> to Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_CMWS1"
                            type="to">Churchill</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d51fn1">Presumably sent to the United States Naval Attaché,
                        London, via Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-06-05">5 June
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>61. Replying to your 63<note n="2" xml:id="d51fn2">
                        <ref target="#d47">document No. 47</ref>.</note> and paragraph 5 of your
                        72<note n="3" xml:id="d51fn3">
                        <ref target="#d50">document No. 50</ref>.</note> in regard to the
                    forthcoming meeting, I find, after full consideration, that July 15 is the
                    earliest date that is practicable for me to attend. Arrangements are therefore
                    being perfected for me to proceed to the vicinity of Berlin to arrive on July
                    15.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . .</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
